      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:53316e58b83c85e3",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: can delve into, kind of condition, authenticity, attribution, provenance. All",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 7831,
        "char_end": 7919,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 398880,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 405560,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:cde38fd08f9e46e6",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The rising prices of dinosaur fossils incentivize more extensive excavation efforts.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.17
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:97b1414674f8b08c",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: prices are hugely increasing the supply of dinosaur fossils.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 9906,
        "char_end": 9977,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 510720,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 515520,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e895d892bc784d64",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "American dinosaur fossils found on private land are legally sellable with landowner permission.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.19
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d21a8de4c8124633",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: permission of all parties, the landowner, the dinosaur hunter, et cetera.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 10927,
        "char_end": 11011,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 568200,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 572800,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:278142bd03f9cf18",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Meticulous due diligence, including GPS coordinates and land deeds, is crucial for verifying fossil provenance.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.24
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:2d95fbedd9a6e03d",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: insist on GPS coordinates.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 13070,
        "char_end": 13107,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 684920,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 688040,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:685db13d27839f69",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: deeds showing that whoever owns it proves their legal title",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 13132,
        "char_end": 13202,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 688080,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 692040,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:70303bf6db36e167",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: of the sale arrangements between the dinosaur hunter and the landowner.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 13275,
        "char_end": 13357,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 696360,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 699880,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:5f84bfee3488c136",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Fossils are rarely discovered intact and are often completed with reconstructed or 3D-printed elements.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.31
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:eb983b7855c78fcd",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: completely intact, virtually never discovered completely intact.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 16929,
        "char_end": 17004,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 894120,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 898800,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:0dcf672d835ae0cf",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: with resin parts or three D printed bones to complete",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17085,
        "char_end": 17149,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 901880,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 906040,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:8128e8f537814ecf",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Transparency regarding the percentage of original bone in a fossil specimen is developing as a market standard.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.32
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:1573d31bfd2cacdb",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: fossil needs to know what they're buying, and that's something",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17217,
        "char_end": 17290,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 910040,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 912920,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:066b03f0dd8eaaef",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: if an element of that bone is present, they'll say, oh, yeah,",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17699,
        "char_end": 17771,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 931400,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 934960,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:60bcab43c8a358d1",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: actually have five percent of that particular bone.",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17964,
        "char_end": 18026,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 942760,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 945960,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0002 - Inside the Booming Market for Dinosaur Fossils_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:f00871f972afbe3b",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 4: a result, a item that looks very complete on a",
        "episode_id": "f7957569-770c-45d3-a4e4-b43c01323ab8",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 18033,
        "char_end": 18090,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 946000,
